### Research Question   ( What is the higher income of movies types to invest in again  ?!)

Conclusions¶

Thriller is the most highest profit genre, following by Adventures and comedy.¶

Drame, Comedy, Thriller and Action are four most-vote genres.¶

The most suitable month to put up and show up the movie is JULY¶

The most unsuitable month for display movie is JANUARY¶

Limitations¶

I am not sure about solution of both question and it is not guaranteed solution without test using statistics¶

During the data cleaning process, I split the data seperated by '|' into lists for easy parsing during the exploration phase. This increases the time taken in calculating the result.¶

For the second question:¶

The adventures movies and thriller is so close to each other in profit value, 
which we cannot not determine the most profit movie type in specific
